snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP drops SURPRISE VIDEO leak exposes AMBER HEARD and her sister's lies and deception
snippet.description:
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #Video

In this episode of Jolly's Rants, Jolly talks about the breaking news in the ongoing court case of Depp vs the Sun.  Reality TV footage was dropped by a source that wants to remain anonymous, exposing a fight between Amber Heard and her sister.
